n Newhouse and Edward Enninful. The edits, which were made in September 202=
3 but apparently noticed only recently by associates of the men, portray En=
ninful=E2=80=99s stint at British Vogue as =E2=80=9Cnot widely seen as a su=
ccess.=E2=80=9D
Curiously, the only other edits Butterfly3232 made were to the bio page of =
Nicholas Coleridge, a real dandy who ran Cond=C3=A9 Nast International prio=
